{
  "text": "Environmental stress tolerance was tested as previously described [CITATION_1] . Briefly, oxygen sensitivity and desiccation was tested by adding cell suspensions of 10 8 cells ml 21 onto microscope coverslips, which were exposed to aerobic conditions or completely dried. After certain time periods, cells were anaerobically resuspended and methane production was checked.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "24909592"
